        <item>
            <title>【CES 2024】Honda 推出 Honda 0 系列概念电动车  「H」品牌标志将于 2026 年启用</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/14/honda-launch-honda-0-series/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=honda-launch-honda-0-series</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/14/honda-launch-honda-0-series/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蒋纳偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 08:24:50 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES 2024]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Honda]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1214874</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Honda 于 2024 年 CES 展会上首次展示了旗下下一代电动车的概念车型——「Honda 0 系列」，预计于 2026 年在美国市场推出。同时，Honda 还推出了专为下一代电动车设计的全新无边框「H 标志」徽章。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1214897" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-32-694x389.png" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-32-694x389.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-32.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1214922" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-44-694x463.png" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-44-694x463.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-44.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1214923" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-45-694x412.png" alt="" width="694" height="412" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-45-694x412.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-45.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Honda 0 系列包括 Saloon 和 Space-Hub 两款概念车，均采用楔形设计，预览了该日本品牌专为电动车打造的下一代车型。Saloon 作为 Honda 0 系列的旗舰车型，拥有宽大、低矮且棱角分明的运动跑车外形。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1214917" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-41-694x461.png" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-41-694x461.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-41.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Honda 表示，Honda 0 系列车型的核心概念是「以人为本/机器为辅」，表明了 Honda 对于驾驶优先、性能和轻量化效率的承诺，尽管车辆配备了被车迷视为对驾驶体验成负面影响的，转向线控技术和基于机器人技术的自动驾驶技术。Honda 承诺，基于 Honda 0 Saloon 概念车的量产车型将于 2026 年推出时，仍将保留「驾驶的乐趣」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1214924" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-46-694x462.png" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-46-694x462.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-46.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Honda 0 系列电动车概念车将配备 e 轴，将电动马达与车轮直接对齐，而不是放在引擎舱内，并配备紧凑、高密度的电池组，以最大化内部空间。Honda 承诺，量产车型将实现「无压力充电」，预计 10 至 15 分钟内可实现 15% 至 80% 的充电，并「最大程度减少电池性能随时间退化」，目标是在 10 年驾驶后电池容量损失不超过 10%。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1214920" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-43-694x462.png" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-43-694x462.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240112at-43.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.cnet.com/roadshow/news/honda-debuts-two-0-series-ev-concepts-aimed-at-2026-production/">cnet</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/rog-phone-8-pro-first-review/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】ROG Phone 8 / 8 Pro　外形　手感　设计　规格开箱评测 + 与 ROG Phone 7 比对</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/09/nvidia-rtx-4070-super-unboxing/parts/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【开箱】NVIDIA RTX 4070 SUPER 显示卡　抢先看 Founder Edition 真身</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/13/invoxia-minitailz/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【CES 2024】测量猫咪狗仔心跳 + 追踪位置   invoxia Minitailz 全新宠物智能颈圈</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/14/honda-launch-honda-0-series/life-tech/auto/">【CES 2024】Honda 推出 Honda 0 系列概念电动车  「H」品牌标志将于 2026 年启用</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
